nents/KanbanBoard.tsx`, `/src/components/BacklogView.tsx`, and `/src/components/IssueDetailDrawer.tsx`.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will create `/src/types.ts` to declare all TypeScript interfaces and type definitions for projects, sprints, issues, comments, sub-tasks, and work logs. This acts as the structural foundation for our modular React workspace."
